{"tid":872330,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"鼻敏感慘過整容失敗","createTime":"2018-10-22T15:18:20.000Z","updateTime":"2018-11-22T05:40:02.000Z","uid":217940,"like":60,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":21,"replies":[{"pid":"4a93965a0d3b90d040cd9460d75258057e6496da","tid":872330,"uid":217940,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:18:20.000Z","msg":"唔知各位明唔明白，<br />\n<br />\n早上一起身就狂打十幾個乞嚏，<br />\n<br />\n仲要唔知敏感源先慘<br />\n<br />\n搭車係咁流鼻水 <br />\n<br />\n身上啲紙巾又用曬 <br />\n<br />\n唯有抬頭扮望嘢<br />\n<br />\n等啲鼻水倒流返去喉嚨到<br />\n<br />\n 之後個喉嚨好痕 就係咁咳<br />\n<br />\n加埋眼搞到浮腫<br />\n<br />\n黑眼圈又大又去唔到"},{"pid":"c2ac973757b3b330fc80b19738273162912bee5b","tid":872330,"uid":134549,"like":14,"dislike":3,"score":11,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:38:02.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"8a13d972f6fb5456da1fc922dd847afebba9d4b4","tid":872330,"uid":21355,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:40:01.000Z","msg":"仲要啲人當你有流感咁"},{"pid":"6bb05219649af42f8b1bfacc450313f6b4ab37d1","tid":872330,"uid":180065,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:41:38.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"d43e5d6d316ea2f9f531f4d2711a926296ddc4ce","tid":872330,"uid":47764,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:43:54.000Z","msg":"i know that feel<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n日日朝早都流鼻水打乞痴 天氣轉就仲嚴重<br />\n又比人以為自己虧 成日病咁 連帶隻眼痕 成日卒眼無精神<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c905404b70e3a1e89bd88f50c35bbab98b42e79f","tid":872330,"uid":143866,"like":1,"dislike":2,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:52:29.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"986973ca3a17147487f5f627de5bf32374992e28","tid":872330,"uid":76692,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T15:54:13.000Z","msg":"一包紙巾傍身 兩包放係袋"},{"pid":"3ccb6f486f74814236969b824c9f485b31265d26","tid":872330,"uid":180065,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T17:57:07.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cf047ae40f5000b14583fc282d0354184ca0444c","tid":872330,"uid":55792,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T18:19:46.000Z","msg":"打乞痴唔好放肆打，要控制下細力啲打<br />\n之前就係覺得大大力打晒出黎好high<br />\n搞到鼻腔鼻竇出血，個醫生仲嚇我話可能生cancer<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n最後食左一個禮拜藥好返"},{"pid":"e39c910afd408680fdd9111f7adc178770320d3b","tid":872330,"uid":133420,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T18:22:40.000Z","msg":"鼻敏感真係好慘，我每日一起身就黎料<br />\n起碼維持到下午 有時去到夜晚<br />\n 最慘係令到黑眼圈更加深，同埋鼻成日甩皮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4a7954b38789d3400aef73e58f31816e42a98f7b","tid":872330,"uid":140309,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T18:27:17.000Z","msg":"same<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我feel到係啱啱起身鼻哥適應唔到溫度轉變而流鼻水<br />\n戴口罩當堂減少流，幾個鐘之後唔流就除得，唯一壞處就係d人成日話我扮病<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n嚴重就食藥加口罩"},{"pid":"71ea602d584bc27b66a3bb2996249130d46c2104","tid":872330,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"見到身邊個個鼻敏感成日要嗦嚟嗦去都sad<br />\n有無辦法幫到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa448e68a8cd0249c241cdbc96a3e02bdc91c1d3","tid":872330,"uid":133420,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"71ea602d584bc27b66a3bb2996249130d46c2104","tid":872330,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T18:33:57.000Z","msg":"見到身邊個個鼻敏感成日要嗦嚟嗦去都sad<br />\n有無辦法幫到佢<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-10-22T18:47:15.000Z","msg":"唔好噴香水<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"894be7392d2b405ff7212a95ddf150d63a5579c9","tid":872330,"uid":3162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"aa448e68a8cd0249c241cdbc96a3e02bdc91c1d3","tid":872330,"uid